drafts.subject: Re: Invitation: Tech conference speaker?
drafts.body:
Subject: Re: Invitation to Speak at Tech Conference

Dear Karen,

Thank you for the invitation to speak at your tech conference. I am very interested in the opportunity.

Could you please provide more details regarding the conference dates, expected audience, and any specific topics you have in mind? This information will help me determine my availability and the most relevant presentation I can offer.

I look forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards,

[Your Name]

action_items: "Confirm interest in speaking at the tech conference by Nov 3."
